{"tid":754461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中銀$100新鈔似陰司紙","createTime":"2018-07-24T12:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T11:26:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1212a4da1eab6070dbef1462eda65d49423af0c2","tid":754461,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180724/large/1532429910_dd9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180724%2Flarge%2F1532429910_dd9c.png&h=706bbc7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事隔8年，本港3間發鈔銀行一同推出新版的20、50、100、500和1,000元鈔票，並首次統一鈔票的設計主題，均印上具香港特色的圖案，其中100元的圖案為粵劇演員，滙豐和渣打的設計，都是男女演員相擁，唯獨中銀僅印上女演員，並佔據鈔票較大面積。不少網民均批評中銀的設計差劣，甚至嘲笑該鈔票看似陰司紙。<br />\n<br />\n至於3間銀行的500元新鈔，均以地質公園的岩石為圖案，惟網民嘲笑中銀的設計，有如電影海報《2012末日預言》世界末日的畫面，相當不吉利，笑言「$500嗰張一定係金融海嘯」。<br />\n網民點睇<br />\n羅冠聰：中銀新推出嘅紙鈔，可以話係有史以來最核突&hellip;&hellip;張100蚊紙簡直直逼恐怖片級數，到底搵咗咩人嚟設計？<br />\nJen Kan：仲醜過冥通<br />\nMay Yuen：其實係想迫大家多用電子支付，少用cash<br />\nSY Woo：大富翁錢仲靚過佢<br />\nHammer Emma：可能畀咗成億設計費，先可以有咁嘅水準<br />\nArgilb Hung：清明重陽驚燒錯<br />\nHamilton Wong Wai Chung：渣打設計的一套，多人氣；中國銀行設計的一套，多鬼氣。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180724/large/1532431633_a241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180724%2Flarge%2F1532431633_a241.jpg&h=d27ec236&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b5d18bf78f00895a7ff88f6c62914c39802c073","tid":754461,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:15:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">中銀1000元新鈔主題係咩？<br />\n市民：醫學相關！！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180724/large/1532432328_b679.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180724%2Flarge%2F1532432328_b679.jpg&h=c8967791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三間發鈔行首公開新鈔設計，市民吳先生表示最喜歡匯豐新鈔的畫風，但覺得三間銀行設計整體大同小異。不過他表示對中銀的設計感到「無語」，當中20元新鈔令他尤其反感：「我唔會想攞住一張咁嘅銀紙，會即刻用左去。」他坦言相較垂直的新設計，比較偏好橫向設計。<br />\n<br />\n市民鄭小姐表示「三款都唔靚，冇一張中意」，她認為100元新鈔設計的粵劇主題最為突出，其餘的都不太明顯。她更誤以為中銀1000元新鈔的主題是與醫學相關，未能聯想到國際金融中心。記者向多名市民查詢中銀1000元新鈔設計主題，無一市民答中。"},{"pid":"65d19d3b88f36ef88a9fb8d19faa7d030805786c","tid":754461,"uid":74171,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:17:35.000Z","msg":"唔覺意燒錯就仆街啦"},{"pid":"af8b68968827b7aac1e816885df5bf519db3f619","tid":754461,"uid":107212,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:19:13.000Z","msg":"中銀呢間野真係垃撚圾<br />\n<br />\n賺咁多錢都唔知用黎做乜"},{"pid":"45e36a69b14c26d809346e78debb678ca7bdce2a","tid":754461,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:19:43.000Z","msg":"左面係家英，右面係明荃。"},{"pid":"f1313bd721cf51f15754237eba0e2bd17a54100a","tid":754461,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:20:41.000Z","msg":"晚麻麻係街地下見到嗰張嘢<br />\n敢唔敢執呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe8ac782b70a31e9e7088006850111558316e85","tid":754461,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:22:12.000Z","msg":"品味呢家野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb65ce48747e277b56b5876d61c1cb6f0b4191b","tid":754461,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:24:28.000Z","msg":"再嘈下次出個共產黨主題"},{"pid":"26db4aa072471fa499baeb2531a3b7ecbe5d5322","tid":754461,"uid":28503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"過左十年 香港d銀紙張張都有習總個麥頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f68b887f5f250c4776de843d67b5c2191649e0a","tid":754461,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:30:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89b840cf4901703c1666b9026d0a040c3f4d28